<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25506</anchor> <rss>anon.142.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Proof</taxon> <addr>anon.142</addr>  <route>anon.142.xml</route>    </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>The univalence property of <tex>A \times  B</tex> follows immediately from that of <tex>A</tex> and <tex>B</tex>.</p>
